'''David Bruce''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

Bruce was inducted into the [[American Contract Bridge League]]'s Hall of Fame in 1997.<ref>{{cite web 
 | title = Hall of Fame
 | author = 
 | publisher = ACBL
 | url = http://www.acbl.org/about/hall-of-fame/members/6
 | date = 
 | accessdate = 2014-10-18 }}</ref>

